Package gov.gsa.pivconformance.cardlib.card.client

Class PIVDataObject

  • java.lang.Object
    • gov.gsa.pivconformance.cardlib.card.client.PIVDataObject
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    BiometricInformationTemplatesGroupTemplate, CardCapabilityContainer, DiscoveryObject, KeyHistoryObject, PairingCodeReferenceDataContainer, PrintedInformation, SecureMessagingCertificateSigner, SignedPIVDataObject, X509CertificateDataObject
    public class PIVDataObject
extends java.lang.Object
    Represents a PIV data object as read to or written from the card. Subclasses may provide abstractions for field access.
